OL,3,CWhat role did women have in
OL,4,CBirmingham's pen industry?
OL,6,FThe museum's patron, Jasper Carrot
OL,7,Fvisited the site to mark the
OL,8,Fcommemorations.
OL,10,FBirmingham's Pen Museum is celebrating
OL,11,F25 years of telling the story of the
OL,12,Fcity's pen trade, which was built on
OL,13,Fthe work of women.
OL,15,FThe celebrations are centering around
OL,16,Fwhat they say is the "unacknowledged
OL,17,Flabour" of women who had a huge part
OL,18,Fto play in the pen trade.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/8
