OL,3,CWhat role did women have in
OL,4,CBirmingham's pen industry?
OL,6,FAt the industry's height, an estimated
OL,7,F8,000 workers were employed, 70% of
OL,8,Fwhich were women.
OL,10,FBirmingham dominated the world's
OL,11,Fproduction of steel pens in the mid-to-
OL,12,Flate 19th century which had a
OL,13,Fsignificant impact on improving on a
OL,14,Fglobal basis.
OL,16,FDuring the industrial peak, there were
OL,17,Fmore than 100 companies manufacturing
OL,18,Fpens in the city.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
