OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1777497069
OL,3,CWhat role did women have in
OL,4,CBirmingham's pen industry?
OL,6,FAs well as employing large numbers of
OL,7,Fpeople, the trade pioneered
OL,8,Fcraftsmanship and manufacturing
OL,9,Fprocesses.
OL,11,FIt represented one of the few
OL,12,Fsubstantial employment opportunities
OL,13,Ffor women outside the textile
OL,14,Findustries in 19th century Britain.
OL,16,FMen were more likely to occupy higher
OL,17,Fpaid skilled positions such as
OL,18,Ftoolmaking or furnace work, whilst
OL,19,Fwomen dominated the production line.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
