OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1777497069
OL,3,CWhat role did women have in
OL,4,CBirmingham's pen industry?
OL,6,FThe museum opened on April 28th 2001
OL,7,Fas the pen room was set up to preserve
OL,8,Fthe city's history, and is based in a
OL,9,Fformer Victorian pen factory.
OL,11,FWhat were the working conditions
OL,12,Finside the factory like?
OL,14,FVal Bache, a volunteer at the museum
OL,15,Fsaid, "When you make a pen here, you
OL,16,Fpull a lever once. The workers did
OL,17,Fthat 18,000 times a day on average,
OL,18,Fone every two seconds.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
