PN,37905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1777497069
OL,3,CWhat role did women have in
OL,4,CBirmingham's pen industry?
OL,6,F"For me being a volunteer is about
OL,7,Fspreading the message that Birmingham
OL,8,Fproduced pens that gave the masses
OL,9,Faccess to literacy."
OL,11,FWomen could earn up to seven shillings
OL,12,Fa week through their work but had to
OL,13,Ffollow strict rules such as no talking
OL,14,Fand no singing.
OL,16,FMistakes, damaged nibs or lateness
OL,17,Fcould result in reduced pay.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
