CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1777497069
OL,3,CWhat role did women have in
OL,4,CBirmingham's pen industry?
OL,6,FWork was typically low-paid,
OL,7,Frepetitive and insecure and women
OL,8,Foperated hand presses for long hours
OL,9,Fand were paid by piece rather than by
OL,10,Ftime.
OL,12,FWomen's roles were also classified as
OL,13,Funskilled, a designation which helped
OL,14,Fto keep wages low.
OL,16,FWhilst many women employed in the pen
OL,17,Ftrade were semi-literate or
OL,18,Filliterate, employers made little
OL,19,Feffort to support education.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
