PN,37907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1777497069
OL,3,CWhat role did women have in
OL,4,CBirmingham's pen industry?
OL,6,FDespite this, women's labour helped
OL,7,Fenable literacy on a global scale by
OL,8,Fproducing cheap, reliable pens for
OL,9,Fmass markets.
OL,11,FThe invention of the ballpoint pen in
OL,12,F1938 signalled the ending for the mass
OL,13,Fproduction of traditional pen nibs and
OL,14,Fby 1950 the biro became cheap and
OL,15,Fconsequently the pen trade went into
OL,16,Fsteep decline.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/8
